<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821379>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2–5. Acmopolynema spp., head except 6. 2, A. sema Schauff, anterior; 3, A. sema Schauff, posterior; 4a, A. varium (Girault), lateral; 4b, A. varium, lateral (internal) showing ocular apodeme; 5, A. varium, dorsal; 6, antennae, lower image medial surface, upper image lateral surface. Scale bars=200 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821379/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821387>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–18. Acmopolynema sp., head. 13, anterior; 14, posterior; 15, lateral; 16, dorsal; 17, ventral; 18, mouthparts. Scale bars=50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821387/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821389>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19–26. Acmopolynema sp., mesosoma or petiole. 19, dorsal; 20, lateral; 21, ventral; 22, anterior; 23, scutellum–propodeum, dorsal; 24, petiole, lateral; 25, petiole, dorsal; 26, petiole, ventral. Scale bars=100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821389/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821381>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7, 8. Acmopolynema spp. 7a, A. varium (Girault), wings; 7b, A. immaculatum Schauff, wings; A. sema Schauff, mesosoma, dorsal. Scale bars: 7=500 μm; 8=200 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821381/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821375>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Acmopolynema varium (Girault), habitus. USA, Virginia, Montgomery Co., 8 km N. Blacksburg, 1–17.viii.1987, CNC Hymenoptera Team. Scale bar=2000 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821375/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821383>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9, 10. Acmopolynema spp. 9, A. varium (Girault), mesosoma + petiole, lateral; 10a, A. sema Schauff, gaster, dorsal; 10b, A. sema Schauff, ovipositor seen through gaster. Scale bars:=200 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821383/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821385>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11, 12. Acmopolynema varium (Girault). 11a, metasoma, lateral; 11b, ovipositor; 12, male metasoma, lateral and genitalia, dorsal. Scale bars=200 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821385/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821391>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27–30. Acmopolynema sp., metasoma. 27, dorsal; 28, ventral; 29, lateral; 30, apex of gaster, lateral. Scale bars: 27–29=100 μm; 30=20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821391/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

